    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Thou Who wast raised up___ on__ the Cross__ of__ Thine own___ will, O Christ our God, do___ Thou__ be-stow__ Thy__ com-pas---sions up-on this, Thy__ new com-mon-wealth___ named___ af-ter__ Thee. Glad--den with Thy__ sov--’reign____ might____ our__ most__ Or--tho--dox hier---archs, and__ vouch-safe them__ vic--to----ry_____ o-ver__ eve--ry__ false teach---ing; and as Thy help in war__ may they pos--sess the weap-on of peace, the tro-phy__ in-vin--ci--ble."
    }
